data.description: The Cali floorplan is one of our most popular designs, with four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car garage. The interior boasts magnificent with wood-look flooring throughout the home. A fantastic open kitchen with a wide island/bar for additional seating, all stainless appliances (including a silent dishwasher, smooth top range, built-in microwave, and plenty of counter space). The covered terrace is located right off the dining room and living room. Bedroom 1 offers a spacious walk-in closet, a lovely adjoining bathroom with a double vanity, a large shower, and an ample linen closet for additional storage. The exterior is low-maintenance and has a two-car garage. Fabric hurricane window protection.  This stunning corner lot home is a must-see.
